<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>ESTP 前额叶恢复 · 专注力重建训练舱</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0b0d12;
    --bg2: #11141c;
    --card: #161a25;
    --line: #232838;
    --text: #e8ecf4;
    --mute: #8a93a8;
    --hot: #ff5a3d;
    --hot2: #ff8a2b;
    --cool: #4dd2ff;
    --good: #38e89a;
    --warn: #ffd166;
    --bad: #ff4f81;
    --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 80% -10%, #1a1f33 0%, var(--bg) 60%) fixed;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 18px 80px; }

  header.hero {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
    padding: 18px 20px; border-radius: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,90,61,.12), rgba(77,210,255,.10));
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  header.hero::after{
    content:""; position:absolute; right:-60px; top:-60px; width:220px; height:220px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,138,43,.35), transparent 60%); filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .title span.tag { font-size: 12px; padding: 3px 8px; margin-left: 8px; background: var(--hot); color:#fff; border-radius: 999px; vertical-align: middle; }
  .subtitle { color: var(--mute); font-size: 13px; }
  .stats { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .pill {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--mute);
  }
  .pill b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }

  nav.tabs {
    display: flex; gap: 6px; margin: 16px 0 14px; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 6px;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  nav.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    background: var(--card); color: var(--mute);
    padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line); cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; user-select: none;
    transition: all .18s ease;
  }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .tab.active {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hot), var(--hot2));
    color: #fff; border-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(255,90,61,.35);
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .card h2 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 17px; }
  .card p.desc { color: var(--mute); font-size: 13px; margin: 0 0 14px; line-height: 1.6; }

  .grid2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  @media (max-width: 720px){ .grid2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  button.btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hot), var(--hot2));
    color: #fff; border: 0; cursor: pointer;
    padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255,90,61,.3);
    transition: transform .08s ease, filter .15s;
  }
  button.btn:active { transform: scale(.97); }
  button.btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.07); }
  button.btn.ghost { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--text); box-shadow: none; }
  button.btn.cool { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a8df0, var(--cool)); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(77,210,255,.25); }
  button.btn.good { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1ea36b, var(--good)); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(56,232,154,.25); }
  .row { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }

  .timer-display { text-align: center; padding: 22px 0 6px; }
  .timer-time {
    font-size: 84px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff, #ffb088);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .timer-phase { color: var(--mute); margin-top: 6px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px; }
  .ring {
    width: 230px; height: 230px; margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: conic-gradient(var(--hot) calc(var(--p,0)*1%), #232838 0);
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    transition: background .4s linear;
  }
  .ring > div { width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--card); display: grid; place-items: center; }
  .preset { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; justify-content: center; }
  .preset .chip {
    padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--mute);
  }
  .preset .chip.active { color: #fff; border-color: var(--hot); background: rgba(255,90,61,.1); }

  .impulse-btn {
    width: 100%; padding: 28px; border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4f81, #ff5a3d);
    color: #fff; border: 0; cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(255,79,129,.4);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
  }
  .impulse-btn:active { transform: scale(.99); }
  .impulse-screen {
    margin-top: 14px; padding: 18px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(255,90,61,.06);
    display: none;
  }
  .impulse-screen.on { display: block; }
  .step-num {
    display: inline-block; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--hot); color: #fff; text-align: center; line-height: 28px;
    font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .impulse-step { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line); }
  .impulse-step:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .countdown { text-align: center; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--warn); margin-top: 8px; }

  .breath-box {
    width: 220px; height: 220px; margin: 8px auto;
    border-radius: 24px; background: rgba(77,210,255,.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(77,210,255,.3);
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    transition: transform 4s ease-in-out, background .4s;
    color: var(--cool); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 4px;
  }

  .ground-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .ground-list li {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .ground-list li .num {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; min-width: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hot), var(--hot2));
    color: #fff; display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 800;
  }
  .ground-list li input {
    flex: 1; background: transparent; border: 0; color: var(--text); font-size: 14px;
    outline: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed transparent; padding: 4px 0;
  }
  .ground-list li input:focus { border-bottom-color: var(--cool); }

  .task-input {
    width: 100%; background: var(--bg2); color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px;
    font-size: 14px; outline: none;
  }
  .task-input:focus { border-color: var(--hot); }
  .task-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 12px 0 0; }
  .task-list li {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .task-list li.done { opacity: .55; }
  .task-list li.done .task-text { text-decoration: line-through; color: var(--mute); }
  .task-list li .task-text { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; }
  .task-list li button { background: transparent; border: 0; color: var(--mute); cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; }
  .check {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border: 2px solid var(--mute);
    cursor: pointer; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .check.on { background: var(--good); border-color: var(--good); }
  .check.on::after { content: "✓"; color: #0b0d12; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; }

  .game-area {
    background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px; min-height: 220px; display: grid; place-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .target {
    width: 84px; height: 84px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--hot) 30%, var(--hot2) 70%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,138,43,.6);
    cursor: pointer; user-select: none;
    display: grid; place-items: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 800;
    transform: scale(1); transition: transform .15s;
  }
  .target:active { transform: scale(.92); }
  .game-stats { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 12px; }
  .game-stats .stat { background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--mute); }
  .game-stats .stat b { color: var(--text); font-size: 14px; }

  .streak-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 6px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .streak-day {
    aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); display: grid; place-items: center;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--mute);
  }
  .streak-day.done { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--good), #1ea36b); color: #0b0d12; font-weight: 800; border-color: transparent; }
  .streak-day.today { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--hot); }

  .about p { line-height: 1.75; color: var(--mute); font-size: 13px; }
  .about strong { color: var(--text); }
  .hide { display: none !important; }

  .toast {
    position: fixed; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity .3s, transform .3s;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 99;
  }
  .toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-4px); }
  footer { text-align: center; color: var(--mute); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="title">前额叶恢复舱 <span class="tag">FOR ESTP</span></div>
    <div class="subtitle">把冲动接回理性 · 把碎片注意力重新焊回一整块</div>
    <div class="stats">
      <span class="pill">今日完成专注 <b id="stat-focus">0</b>
